{"tid":930004,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel推首部華人超級英雄電影《Shang-Chi》 由TVB巨星演出？！","createTime":"2018-12-06T03:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T11:47:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"51b1a847a45510b9824d011b1e16f3a0611aab79","tid":930004,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"Marvel迷最近都好忙，事關不斷有超級英雄電影的相關消息出現，同時英雄電影又真的是長拍長有。近日Marvel才推出了首部女性超級英雄電影《Marvel隊長》的第二彈預告，當大家還期待《Marvel隊長》和《復仇者4》的關係時，有外國媒體報導Marvel Studio將拍攝首部華人超級英雄電影《Shang-Chi》（上氣）！<br />\n<br />\n漫畫中Shang-Chi是反派Dr. Fu Manchu（傅滿洲）的兒子，本替他做事，後來改邪歸正。而電影版還在劇本創作的階段，Marvel找來寫《神奇女俠1984》的編劇Dave Callaham來寫。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出就引來不少粉絲猜測會由誰來演，比較多人希望由吳彥祖、彭于晏、吳京、張晉等大名氣華裔演員演出。<br />\n<br />\n但筆者在Google一搜尋，發現是由馬浚偉飾演！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-04-4.47.17_17292531745c0641b064bc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-04-4.47.17_17292531745c0641b064bc0.jpg&h=bca11bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-05-4.18.52_15203581715c0789fa8aa0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-05-4.18.52_15203581715c0789fa8aa0f.jpg&h=7f2b2250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/328730/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e5%a8%9b%e8%81%9e/shang-chi-marvel%e9%9a%8a%e9%95%b7-%e5%be%a9%e4%bb%87%e8%80%85/5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F328730%2F%25e6%259c%2580%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%25a8%259b%25e8%2581%259e%2Fshang-chi-marvel%25e9%259a%258a%25e9%2595%25b7-%25e5%25be%25a9%25e4%25bb%2587%25e8%2580%2585%2F5%2F&d=25lWIakmnjXfrruxfuQJpV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7e326367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/328730/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e5%a8%9b%e8%81%9e/shang-chi-marvel%e9%9a%8a%e9%95%b7-%e5%be%a9%e4%bb%87%e8%80%85/5/</a>"},{"pid":"7c98a6c36f02e9692b24000de319ccdce75246df","tid":930004,"uid":176802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑咗"},{"pid":"4bbe8931f9b5517e4338d44a28d16c354e28a893","tid":930004,"uid":137999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"鐵血保鑣已經有漫威既人物"},{"pid":"6a113c529cd4301d0d8cf761c6d9c269bcd866fd","tid":930004,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"契哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4b86f3111d553f0b1ccb5ecf2b6c349614a649","tid":930004,"uid":33907,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:20:43.000Z","msg":"笑到我上氣唔接下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3416bbb5defeb9733e5aa3bfd5d20b82be715c9e","tid":930004,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493644da860aa480693e70a50a79b2f4cb551550","tid":930004,"uid":16777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"伍允龍做應該都唔錯<br />\n打又得 英文又得"},{"pid":"ed09d7f3943d9f02775c75116951df44f5a41ef0","tid":930004,"uid":132201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"生滋"},{"pid":"3ef0a5bea3bda6c8329835f389a20734554c8639","tid":930004,"uid":84250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"安志杰/伍允龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" 